WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.800
Stop babysitting AI coding work.
AI coding does not lack models.
It lacks a command tower.

00:03.800 --> 00:07.800
See the live board before you trust the run.
PM request, Command Tower, Workflow Cases,
and Proof and Replay stay inside
one governed loop.

00:07.800 --> 00:11.000
Keep blocker risk and proof readiness in view.
Track live work, queue posture, blocker risk,
and replay-ready evidence before promotion or rerun.

00:11.000 --> 00:14.000
The macOS desktop shell mirrors the same command tower.
Keep the PM flow, hotkeys,
drawers, and proof surfaces aligned in a native shell.

00:14.000 --> 00:18.000
Inspect before you trust.
Repo-backed today. Start with one proven workflow.
Keep the boundary truthful, then choose
the adoption path that matches the real job.
